<li>Roan, Sharon (1990). Ozone Crisis, the 15 Year Evolution of a Sudden Global Emergency. Wiley. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0471528234" class="internal">ISBN 0-471-52823-4</a></li>
<li>Cagin, Seth and Dray, Phillip (1993). Between Earth and Sky: How CFCs Changed Our World and Endangered the Ozone Layer. Pantheon. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0679420525" class="internal">ISBN 0-679-42052-5</a></li>
</ul>
