<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Ozone_depletion&amp;action=edit&amp;section=31" title="Edit section: Books on public policy issues">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Books on public policy issues</span></h3>
<ul>
